<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en-US">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<script type="text/javascript" src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.6.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
	<%= javascript_include_tag "cufon" %>
	<%= javascript_include_tag "fonts/Mensch_400.font.js" %>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		Cufon.replace('h1'); // Works without a selector engine
		Cufon.replace('h2'); // Requires a selector engine for IE 6-7, see above
		Cufon.replace('p');
	</script>

	<title>Hostee | Easy Domain &amp; Hosting Billing Cycle Management</title>

	<%= stylesheet_link_tag "teaser" %>
	
</head>

<body>

	<div id="branding">
		<img src="/images/hostee.png" border="0"  align=center style="margin:auto; align:center;">
	</div><!-- #header -->

	<div id="main">

		<div id="container">
			<div id="content" role="main">
			<h1>Fast and easy domain and hosting billing management</h1>
			
			<p>
				Keeping track of all your clients domains and hosting cycles can be a bit of a pain. Hostee is being designed to change that.<br>Hostee will keep on top of all your billing cycles and manage them for you, leaving you more time to do the things you enjoy
			</p>
			
			<% if @saved != true %>
				<p>Are you as excited as we are about Hostee.  <br>Join our mailing list and we'll let you know the instant it's ready</p>
				
				<% form_for :maillist do |list| %>
					<input type=search name="maillist[email]" id="maillist_email" value="" placeholder="Enter your e-mail address" style="text-align:center;width:300px; font-size:16px;"><br>
					<input type=submit value="Let me know when it's ready" class="action-button" onmousedown="this.className='action-button-focus'" onmouseup="this.className='action-button'" onmouseout="this.className='action-button'">
				<% end %>
				</div><!-- #wrapper -->
			<% else %>
				<p style="font-size:24px">Now we have your email we will let you know as soon as its ready</p>
			<% end %>
	</div>
	
	<div id="footer" style="width:100%;">
		<div>
			<h2>Follow Us Via: <a href="http://www.twitter.com/hosteeapp"><img src="/images/twittericon.png" style="display:inline;padding-top:5px;"> Twitter</a> <a href="http://blog.hosteeapp.co.uk"><img src="/images/wordpress-icon.png" style="display:inline;padding-top:5px;"> Blog</a> </h2> 
			<h2>Copyright 2011</h2>
		</div>
	</div>


	<script type="text/javascript"> Cufon.now(); </script>
</body>
</html>